    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people who passed driving test in automatic car to drive manual cars",
        "additional_details": "Because most electric cars are automatic, we don't want people who passed their driving test in a modern, automatic car to be prevented from driving manual cars.",
        "background": "We want the Government to allow people who passed their driving test in automatic car to drive manual cars. People who passed their test in a manual car can drive automatics, and we think the reverse should be allowed too.",
